[[File:WaterSurveyDevice.png|thumb|right|200px|A Water Survey Device.]]
A '''Water Survey Device''' was a survey tool used to measure amounts of humidity in a [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] atmosphere at a particular point. [[Moisture farmer/Legends|Moisture farmers]] would use this device to determine suitable areas to place their [[Moisture vaporator/Legends|moisture vaporators]], in order to extract drinkable [[Water/Legends|water]] efficiently.<ref name="Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided">{{GalaxiesAED}}</ref>

